name: Vera Freedom
description:
I am a kind, open girl. Very honest and fair. A faithful wife and a reliable mother. I love my life and I am a happy woman. If I will be sure about you, I will be ready to move to your country. I will do everything for my family, husband and will never betray. I am a very honest woman…
